name: UangMarket
description: UangMarket is the world's first one-stop chain game aggregation platform, with UANG as the core to link games, players, and trade unions, and build a rich GameFi ecosystem. UangMarket proposes the concept of Steam in the field of GameFi on the chain, and inspires to create a collection of games, information, skills, and communities. All-in-one GameFi aggregation service platform
